data.description: Welcome to 215 Oakwood Ln. in the heart of Bloomingdale, Illinois, nestled within the desirable Westlake townhome subdivision. This remarkable townhome boasts three spacious bedrooms, one and a half bathrooms, and a generous 1,700 square feet of living space. Step inside and discover the perfect space for your personal entertainment needs in the finished basement, a canvas for your creativity. Convenience abounds with a full-size laundry room in the basement, ideal for additional storage or an extra refrigerator. For just $200 a month in association dues, you'll enjoy exclusive access to incredible amenities, including an indoor pool, tennis court, clubhouse, and a party room-making every day feel like a vacation. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring an inviting eat-in area and an abundance of cabinets and drawers to neatly store all your culinary essentials. Don't wait! This home is priced to sell by a motivated seller in one of Bloomingdale's most sought-after areas. Seize the opportunity to make 215 Oakwood Ln. your new home sweet home today!
